CustomField.description: Indicates whether the payee influenced a higher rate of employer Superannuation. If 'Yes' is selected any employer superannuation above the standard rate will be calculated separately and reported as RESC.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If the field is left blank, the Employer Contribution will report in the SGC field for SuperStream Reports, however if it is populated with 'No' the amount will report in the Award field for Superstream Reports. If populated with 'Yes' it will report in the RESC field for Superstream Reporting.
CustomField.label: Employee Influenced Super Variation
